{"tid":1718965,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再講咩和理非同勇武","createTime":"2019-11-14T03:34:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T03:36:26.000Z","uid":114873,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f0a73e27c7ef40e5f5831e3f9fe14251df043a00","tid":1718965,"uid":114873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:34:03.000Z","msg":"由1111開始，香港已經進入<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">戰爭</span></span>狀態<br />\n<br />\n發生衝突嘅地方唔再係發生衝突，而係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">戰場</span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以冇必要再分和理非定勇武，你上得戰場嘅就係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">士兵</span></span>，上得場就預咗會死<br />\n<br />\n警方同政權就係我地嘅敵人，俾敵人拉咗我地就係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">俘虜</span></span>。放得返出黎係敵人嘅愚蠢。<br />\n<br />\n唔該所有人有戰爭意識，迫使香港進入緊急狀態，全面停工停課。咁樣嘅話唔再需要成日吹雞要人，我地可以實行<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">徵兵制</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n最重要一點，唔好再有道德綁架。港共政權已經全面宣戰，敵方不斷從其他紀律部隊、甚至退休狗落手擴充軍隊編制，我方必須成立<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">民兵隊</span></span>。裝備係當務之急。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">搶又好，自製又好。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人，打勝仗！</span></span>"},{"pid":"4dce1c51be3e266da14a4565cda91bef2c542e5d","tid":1718965,"uid":114873,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:36:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">The World War III has begun</span></span>"}]}